$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_reference

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_reference -  This method returns the reference string to use in the player's refer, even when they are off line.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string query_reference(string name)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the player
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the reference string or 0, if none

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/player_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the reference string to use in the player's refer,
even when they are off line.
.EP

